== 製作 ==
=== 發展 ===
《超吉任務》是由湯姆·葛米根（{{lang|en|Tom Gormican}}）和{{le|凱文·艾登|Kevin Etten}}共同創作的劇本，於2019年11月15日被[[狮门娱乐|獅門]]收購；葛米根擔任導演，艾登透過製片商土星影業（{{lang|en|Saturn Films}}）與凱文·圖倫（{{lang|en|Kevin Turen}}）、[[尼可拉斯·凱吉|尼可拉斯·凱吉]]與邁克·尼龍（{{lang|en|Mike Nilon}}）共同擔任製片。凱吉在片中以本人的身份出演，劇情描述急需用錢的他勉強接受了100萬美元的邀請，以參加墨西哥億萬富翁超級粉絲生日。當事情變得瘋狂時，凱吉被迫擔任起電影英雄式的角色，以使自己擺脫日益危險的境地。<ref name="THR(2019-11-15)">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/nicolas-cage-star-as-nicolas-cage-unbearable-weight-massive-talent-1254626|title=Nicolas Cage in Talks to Star as Nicolas Cage in Meta Drama 'The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent' (Exclusive)|last=Kit|first=Borys|work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2019-11-15|accessdate=2020-12-07}}</ref><ref name="Deadline(2019-11-15)">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/nicolas-cage-movie-the-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent-movie-lionsgate-1202787717/|title=Nicolas Cage Pic ‘The Unbearable Weight Of Massive Talent’ Near Lionsgate Deal|last1=Hipes|first1=Patrick|last2=D'Alessandro|first2=Anthony|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2019-11-15|accessdate=2020-12-07|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029140102/https://deadline.com/2019/11/nicolas-cage-movie-the-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent-movie-lionsgate-1202787717/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 選角 ===
