eight Of Massive Talent’ For Lionsgate|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2020-11-23|accessdate=2020-12-07}}</ref><ref name="CBR(2020-11-24)">{{cite news|url=https://www.cbr.com/nicolas-cage-movie-neil-patrick-harris/|title=Nicolas Cage's Nicolas Cage Movie Casts Neil Patrick Harris|last=Laman|first=Douglas|work={{le|漫畫書資源網|Comic Book Resources|CBR}}|date=2020-11-24|accessdate=2020-12-07}}</ref>。

