== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《超吉任務》在業界口碑優良。評論匯總網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據288條評論，本片獲得86%的新鮮度，均分7.2／10。該網站共識：「《超吉任務》以聰明、有趣、極富創造力的形式呈現了尼可拉斯·凱吉的怪奇巔峰，佩德羅·帕斯卡的搶鏡演出更與他相得益彰。」<ref name="RT">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_unbearable_weight_of_massive_talent|title=The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent (2022)|work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=[[Fandango_(公司)|Fandango Media]]|accessdate=2022-03-19}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上根據52條評論，獲得68分，屬「普遍好評」<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent|title=The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2022-03-19}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在美國及加拿大，《超吉任務》與《[[壞蛋聯盟|壞蛋聯盟]]》、《[[北方人_(電影)|北方人]]》同天上映並競爭，預計首映週末能在3036間影院獲得500萬至1000萬美元的票房<ref name="Variety(2022-04-20)">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2022/film/box-office/box-office-bad-guys-northman-unbearable-weight-opening-weekend-1235237068/ |title=Box Office: ''The Bad Guys'', Viking Epic ''The Northman'' and Nicolas Cage's ''Massive Talent'' to Battle ''Fantastic Beasts 3''|first=Rebecca|last=Rubin|work=Variety|date=2022-04-20|accessdate=2022-04-20}}</ref><ref name="Deadline(2022-04-20)">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2022/04/box-office-northman-bad-guys-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent-nicolas-cage-1235006554/|title=''Bad Guys'', ''The Northman'' & ''Unbearable Weight Of Massive Talent'' Look To Provide Breadth At Weekend Box Office|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2022-04-20|accessdate=2022-04-21}}</ref><ref name="Deadline(2022-04-20)-2">{{cite web|url=https://www.boxofficepro.com/weekend-box-office-forecast-the-bad-guys-the-northman-and-the-unbearable-weight-of-massive-talent/|title=Weekend Box Office Forecast: ''The Bad Guys'', ''The Northman'', and ''The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent'' Take on ''Sonic 2'' and ''Dumbledore'' (Updated)|first=Shawn|last=Robbins|work={{le|Boxoffice Pro|Boxoffice Pro}}|date=2022-04-20|accessdate=2022-04-22}}</ref>。本片首日進帳290萬美元，週四晚間預售達83.5萬美元；上映首週開盤710萬美元，位居當週票房排名第五。[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]點評，《超吉任務》和《北方人》主打客群重疊，導致開盤表現受影響；該網站更提及上映時的低知名度以及凱吉缺乏經營社交媒體是本片票房表現不佳的原因。上映首週期間，59%的觀眾是男性，其中18至34歲年齡段的觀眾佔電影票銷售額的57%。<ref name="opening" />

